com.hazelcast.internal.cluster.impl

Class MembersView

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.internal.cluster.impl.MembersView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable, Versioned

    public final class MembersView
extends Object
implements IdentifiedDataSerializable, Versioned
    MembersView is a container object to carry member list and version together. MembersView implements Versioned because it serializes versioned objects (MemberInfo) by passing its own ObjectDataOutput to internal objects' writeData method.
